# Pokemon Price Tracker — graded card prices (PSA, CGC, BGS)
# Free tier: 100 lookups/day, no commercial use (dev only).
# Business tier ($99/mo): commercial use OK, 200K credits/day — required for mainnet flip.
# Sign up at https://www.pokemonpricetracker.com/pokemon-card-price-api
POKEMON_PRICE_TRACKER_API_KEY=

# Agent Server
